WhatsApp Message Analysis (Marathi/Hindi) 📊📱
📌 About the Project
This project is a WhatsApp Chat Analyzer that extracts useful insights from WhatsApp conversations. It supports Marathi and Hindi languages by filtering out common stopwords and provides meaningful data visualizations.

🔍 Features
✅ Message Statistics – Total messages, words, media files, and links shared.
✅ Word Cloud – Highlights the most frequently used words while filtering stopwords.
✅ Most Common Words – Identifies the top frequently used words.
✅ Emoji Analysis – Displays the most used emojis in the chat.
✅ User Activity Analysis – Shows the most active users in group chats.
✅ Monthly & Daily Trends – Helps track chat activity over time.
✅ Heatmap of Chat Activity – Visualizes chat frequency based on time of the day.

📦 Tech Stack Used
🟢 Python – Core programming language
🟢 Streamlit – For creating an interactive web application
🟢 Pandas – Data processing and manipulation
🟢 Matplotlib & Seaborn – Data visualization
🟢 WordCloud – Generating word cloud visualizations
🟢 NLTK – Handling stopwords
🟢 Emoji – Extracting and analyzing emoji usage

🚀 How to Use?
1️⃣ Upload a WhatsApp chat file (.txt) from your phone.
2️⃣ Select User (or analyze overall chat).
3️⃣ Explore Insights through graphs, word clouds, and tables.
